# VHS Tape (see https://github.com/charmbracelet/vhs)
Output "target/stopwatch.gif"
Set Theme "Aardvark Blue"
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Hide
Type@0 "cargo run -p tui-big-text --example stopwatch --quiet"
Enter
Sleep 2s
Show
Sleep 2s
Space@2s 5
Space@1s 5
Space@0.5s 10
Space@0.25s 20
Enter
Sleep 2s
